p pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_38\" title=\"Chapter 38\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_40\" title=\"Chapter 40\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>Chapter 39</b> is titled \"For Whom the Bell Tolls\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy%27s_Crew_Adventure_Chronicles\" title=\"Buggy&#39;s Crew Adventure Chronicles\">Buggy's Crew Adventure Chronicles</a>, Vol. 4: \"<a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a> and the <a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/East_Blue_Saga#Big_Bird\" title=\"Animal Species/East Blue Saga\">Big Bird</a>\"\n</p><p>Finding that the chicks he planned to eat are protected by a <a href=\"/wiki/Big_Bird\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Big Bird\">huge parent</a> who intends to eat <i>him</i>, <a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a> runs away in terror.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">Kuro</a> continues attacking his crew until Luffy tells him to fight him instead. Luffy ends up wrapping his elongated limbs around Kuro so that he cannot escape and wins their fight by using a headbutt. At the same time, <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a> is about to kill <a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> after beating <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a>. But <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> intervene and save Kaya from Jango.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> are still watching as Kuro continues to cut up the other <a href=\"/wiki/Black_Cat_Pirates\" title=\"Black Cat Pirates\">Black Cat Pirates</a>. Suddenly, Luffy is wounded by Kuro but he keeps his ground and grabs Kuro's jacket and throws him to the ground. Kuro mocks Luffy, saying he should have stood still so Kuro could kill him easier, and because Luffy stops him moving, his crew are still alive and suffering. Kuro goes to do his move again, but this time Luffy grabs him and holds him tight. Kuro is unable to move.\n</p><p>In the forest, <a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> agrees to sign the will if Jango stops hurting the <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a> throws them against trees and turns to Kaya, who has his hypnotizing ring and threatens to kill herself with it if he does not do what she says. Jango panics, because if he does not get the will signed before her death he is in trouble. While Kaya signs the will, the Usopp pirates pretend to be hurt. They discuss their options and agree that just because their losing does not mean they can run away. With the will signed, Jango now prepares himself to kill Kaya.\n</p><p>Zoro and <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> spot them. Zoro tosses Usopp aside to stop Jango. As Jango goes in for the kill the Usopp Pirates ram a shovel between the cheeks of his rear. Angrily he kicks them aside and goes to kill Kaya, stating to Zoro he is too late to save her. But Zoro states it wasn't his goal to do so, he cuts some branches blocking a clear shot of Jango from Usopp. With the branches out of the way, Usopp now can fire a clear shot at Jango with his <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp%27s_Arsenal/Ginga_Pachinko\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Usopp&#39;s Arsenal/Ginga Pachinko\">slingshot</a>.\n</p><p>Back at the coastline, Kuro's crew cheer Luffy on. Luffy throws his head back and stretches his neck far enough back to tell the Black Cat pirates to stop cheering for him. Kuro in shock just keeps on about how his plan will not fail.\n</p><p>Jango is hit by Usopp's slingshot and at that same moment, Kuro also falls as Luffy pulls his head back and rams it into Kuro.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> makes a deal with <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a>; to sign the will if he stops hurting the Usopp Pirates.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> stop <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a>.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/wiki/Black_Cat_Pirates\" title=\"Black Cat Pirates\">Black Cat Pirates</a> begin to cheer for <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a>.\n<ul><li>However, <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> tells them not to cheer for him and that they're next after he beats their <a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">captain</a>.</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species\" title=\"Animal Species\">Animals</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy_Pirates\" title=\"Buggy Pirates\">Buggy Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">Buggy</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Black_Cat_Pirates\" title=\"Black Cat Pirates\">Black Cat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">Kuro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Syrup_Village\" title=\"Syrup Village\">Syrup Village</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Piiman\" title=\"Piiman\">Piiman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ninjin\" title=\"Ninjin\">Ninjin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tamanegi\" title=\"Tamanegi\">Tamanegi</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/East_Blue_Saga#Big_Bird\" title=\"Animal Species/East Blue Saga\">Big Bird</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/East_Blue_Saga#Big_Bird\" title=\"Animal Species/East Blue Saga\">Big Bird's Children</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nAt last it's here, the season of warmth. For a lazy guy like me, getting along by wearing just a t-shirt is too awesome to handle.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nやってきましたあたたかなこの季節。Tシャツ1枚で過ごせる手軽さが不精な僕にはたまらない。</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>This chapter's title may be a reference to the book \"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/For_Whom_the_Bell_Tolls\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:For Whom the Bell Tolls\">For Whom the Bell Tolls</a>\" by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Hemingway\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Ernest Hemingway\">Ernest Hemingway</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_39%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_38\" title=\"Chapter 38\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_40\" title=\"Chapter 40\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; font-size:90%; clear:both; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"cs EastBlueSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Syrup_Village_Arc\" title=\"Syrup Village Arc\">Syrup Village Arc</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"cs EastBlueSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Syrup_Village_Arc_Chapters\" title=\"Category:Syrup Village Arc Chapters\">Manga Chapters</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_22\" title=\"Chapter 22\">22</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_23\" title=\"Chapter 23\">23</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_24\" title=\"Chapter 24\">24</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_25\" title=\"Chapter